<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login Form</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body data-page="login">
    <div class="parent-container parent-login">

        <div class="visual-container">
            <img class="align-center" src="/images/note.png" alt="Note Image">

            <h3 class="primary-text heading-text align-center">Bienvenue Folk!</h3>
            <p class="primary-text align-center">Salut! Ça va bien? Task management is essential when there are too many unfinished tasks. Don't worry anymore! 'Tasks Très Bien' is here to help you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="form-wrapper">
            <div class="form-container">
                <h3 class="text-center mb-4 primary-text heading-text">Login</h3>

                <form id="loginForm" action="/login" method="post">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="username" class="form-label primary-text">Username</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control primary-text black-text" name="username" id="login-username" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="password" class="form-label primary-text">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" id="login-password" required>
                    </div>

                    <p class="align-right primary-small-text font-italic" onclick="openForgotPasswordPopup()">
                        Forgot password?
                    </p>

                    <button type="submit" class="primary-text white-text btn btn-primary w-100">Login</button>

                    <div class="divider">
                        <span>or</span>
                    </div>

                    <p class="primary-small-text align-center">New Tasker? 
                        <a class="primary-small-text font-bold-italic" href="/signup">Create Account</a>
                    </p>

                    <% if (error) { %>
                        <p class="primary-small-text red-icon align-center"><%= error %></p>
                    <% } %>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div id="forgotPasswordPopup" class="popup-overlay">
        <div class="popup-content">
            <span class="close-btn" onclick="closePopup('forgotPasswordPopup')">&times;</span>
            <p class="primary-text black-text align-left">Dear Customer,<br><br>Unfortunately, You have to remember your password. We can't do anything for you in this case.(or anyother case either)<br>But FORTUNATELY, if you totally forgot the password, you can go create a new account. Or do anything else you like. We're always here for you, trying to develop user-centered designs, but just trying only, not doing anything. Any ideas from you, our dear customer, is warmly welcomed, but we will not follow your idea no matter what *^^*.<br>Hope you have best day!<br><br>Yours User-friendly, User-experience-centered developer,<br>Myat</p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
